$SUBROUTINE ADVAN4 TRANS4 $PK TVKA=THETA(1) TVV2=THETA(2) TVCL=THETA(3) TVV3=THETA(4) TVQ=THETA(5)

IF (IPRED.GT.1) THEN W = SQRT(IPRED**2*SIGMA(1,1) + SIGMA(2,2)) ELSE W=1 ENDIF
IWRES=IRES/W Y=F+F*ERR(1)+ERR(2)
